# Personal Expense Tracker (Python CLI Project)

A beginner-friendly **Python command-line application** to track your daily expenses. This tool allows you to add expenses, view all transactions, generate monthly reports, and visualize spending categories using pie charts.

---

## Features

- Add new expense entries with date, category, amount, and description
- View all recorded expenses from a CSV file
- Generate monthly expense reports
- Visualize category-wise expense breakdown using a pie chart
- Stores all data in a `CSV` file
- Uses `DD-MM-YYYY` date format


